track_notes: Starting from the village Touet sur Var, the walk is a bit long. No much room on summit as you are in forest wood
Starting on the D27, where you can park, you will have to find a path to the summit in the forest. There is a cairn on trig point, no so easy to find.

You can park at the village Rourebel (10 cars). The path is very difficult to found, it is the third attempt and i am still looking for the good way.
I am not sure that the summit is located at the good place. I will try next time to reach a place a bit further on the crest.
